Section::::Electrolysis .
About four percent of hydrogen gas produced worldwide is created by electrolysis .
The majority of this hydrogen produced through electrolysis is a side product in the production of chlorine .
* 2 NaCl(aq ) + 2 HO(l ) → 2 NaOH(aq )
